							Informations pratiques
						</button><div id="tip-tab-liens-sp-LEGIARTI000006224934-28" class="tabs-secondary-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="hidden-element js-first" tabindex="-1">Informations pratiques</div><div id="tip-tab-liens-sp-LEGIARTI000006224934-28-content" class="loader"></div></div></div></div></article></li><li class="opened" data-a="false"><article class="js-child list-article-consommation"><div data-a="false"><div><p class="name-article" data-anchor="LEGIARTI000006224947" id="LEGIARTI000006224947-29"><a href="/codes/article_lc/LEGIARTI000006224947/2023-08-03" id="linkLEGIARTI000006224947-29" >Article L225-118</a></div><div class="content"><p>Le droit à communication des documents, prévu aux <a href='/affichCodeArticle.do?cidTexte=LEGITEXT000005634379&idArticle=LEGIARTI000006224907&dateTexte=&categorieLien=cid' title='Code de commerce - art. L225-115 (V)'>articles L. 225-115, L. 225-116 et L. 225-117</a>, appartient également à chacun des copropriétaires d'actions indivises, au nu-propriétaire et à l'usufruitier d'actions.</div><div class="tabs-secondary tabs-main"><button class="js-tab-secondary tabs__link ajax-load-tab-revision tab-first-order" tabindex="0" data-textecid="LEGITEXT000005634379" data-articlecid="LEGIARTI000006224947" data-articleid="LEGIARTI000006224947" data-num="L225-118" aria-expanded="false" id="tip-tab-revision-LEGIARTI000006224947-29-button" data-tip="tip-tab-revision-LEGIARTI000006224947-29" data-fond="CODE" aria-describedby="LEGIARTI000006224947-29" data-complement="-29" data-abrogated="false" onclick="eulerianClick(this, 'Versions')">
                    		Versions
